\contentsline {table}{\numberline {5.3}{\ignorespaces Landmark latency and accuracy on Redmi at BS=1 with XNNPACK. LM inf. means landmark inference and ms means milliseconds. Bold values mark the lower latency and lower error within each model pair.}}{27}{table.caption.17}%
