\contentsline {table}{\numberline {5.6}{\ignorespaces Landmark-inference latency batch scaling for PipNet-R18 with INT8 XNNPACK across three devices; lower is better. Bold marks the best value in each batch-size column.}}{30}{table.caption.22}%
